# Pixel Art

## cyberpunk-city.png

A 64x64 pixel art depiction of a cyberpunk cityscape at night, featuring neon-lit skyscrapers, holographic billboards, and a glowing moon. 

Created to represent the vibrant, futuristic spirit of collaborative software development and the creative potential of AI-human partnerships in open source.
